reviewText:
I am a 32nd degree Master Mason.  I'm glad the History Channel chose to make a documentary on Masonry.  But this one is a huge pile of smelly crap.  Masons chanting around a severed cow head in a dark field?  Whatever...
If you want to know the real deal, before actually joining, read Freemasons for Dummies.  I give it my full endorsement.
